title: (x) YCN Compressed Sans Font - Roswell Four {Jim}
content:
Hi,

I love the idiosyncratic compressed sans YCN are using, does anyone know what it is?

[http://72rivingtonstreet.com/images/structure/logo.png](http://web.archive.org/web/20131012091715/http:/72rivingtonstreet.com/images/structure/logo.png "http://72rivingtonstreet.com/images/structure/logo.png")

I can scan in a paper copy if anyone needs it a little larger, but it's quite distinct so I imagine one of you geniuses will know.

Thanks

Jono
